title: 2021 CFB Pick Em Week 4
description:
El Pres, Big Cat & Rico Bosco are back for another week of picks. Hot off a Pick Em Parlay win this weekend, Rico was "mopey" for some reason. We introduced Angelina, our new FCS specialist to the podcast and Jersey Jerry made an urgent call to Big Cat.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
